index.content: You're invited! Open House Reception July 22nd, 2017 3pm-7pm 15005 SW Chardonnay Ave.Tigard, OR 97224 Click here to copy address! Registery Your presence is what we desire the most, but if you would like to help us furnish our new home, our registries are below. We will have a way to transport gifts from Portland to our home in L.A. Please RSVP by July 16th.
